. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"9fb904d637587ccee67ae8ec71b9ed4806e4a232","tid":1553783,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b05db9c872d123cece711ae12317a31d8d1da3da","tid":1553783,"uid":37396,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:30:50.000Z","msg":"所以唔好鬧今日舉TRUMP 牌啲人<br />\n侵仔都好重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKFXSD2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKFXSD2.png&h=a3b8bc20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直接講美國就議員總統都包哂<br />\n又唔會得失人"},{"pid":"0ccc2ec794b8d966e4487c17e60a7099db5e5072","tid":1553783,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee3fa1997f09ffedb6479ef829fd16ed062c2f73","tid":1553783,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c94757047698a2a0838d053c4faa97607817b5ff","tid":1553783,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09e2a05c63bdf23519a0aab85594a068707cc7b8","tid":1553783,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:18:56.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n一半就得，但要侵侵簽名<br />\n2/3就冇得侵侵拒絕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"咁都好似未可以好老定wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"梗係唔可以老定啦，靜靜地贏plz"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"大家繼續諗吓如果唔通過，或者通過咗但係中共繼續亂捉人點算。而家嘅問題係，有人消失咗，中共可以話係佢去咗罷工罷課，或者偷偷地去咗外國。噉就冇證據話佢係被消失。要自衛呀。<br />\n🍮🍮🍮"},{"pid":"802efb4dda8bbb693250b6dcdb483fd8b08c2ced","tid